HEADWORD: cocksucker
<hw>cock"suck*er</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a worthless or despicable
person; -- intended as disparaging and invariably offensive.</def>
<mark>[vulgar slang]</mark>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> rotter, rat, skunk, stinker, bum, crumb, lowlife,
scum bag, motherfucker, mother.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>a person who performs fellatio.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

